                    <fieldText>&lt;p&gt;&lt;i style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Before you progress to the&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;Negotiation/Review&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;stage, you must complete appropriate due diligence on all potential partners/funders.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</fieldText>
