                <fields>
                    <name>Q4_dtxt_n</name>
                    <fieldText>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Q4 - Has the possible partner(s) said or done anything in the course of interactions with Monash that could&amp;nbsp;be construed as &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.monash.edu/__data/assets/pdf_file/0011/781175/Fraud-and-Corruption-Policy.pdf&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(5, 99, 193);&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;corruption or suggestive of corrupt inten&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;t? If yes, please describe:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</fieldText>
